tafsir[40]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,"Ko Й“ee sirkuЙ“e naamnandirta caggal de Alla neli e mum en nelaaЙ—o Makko-yo o his-"
  78,2,"HoЙ“e naamnandira kabaaru mawЙ—o on, oon woni Quraana tedduЙ—o tellinaaЙ—o e nelaaЙ—o mum en coomЙ—o kabaaru ummital."
  78,3,"O Quraana mbo Й“e luuri e mum e koЙ“e cifatoo mbo ko, wonde kombo mbilewu wolla jime wollo wageyaagal wolla tinndi adiiЙ“e."
  78,4,"Wonah noЙ“e ngaaЖҙarii nih, Й“ee fennuЙ“e qurana maЙ“e nganndu batte pennugol maЙ“Й“e bonngol."
  78,5,"Refti teentana Й“e Й—uum."
  78,6,"Mbela Min mbattaani leydi ndi keblaandi wonande Й“e, lobbundi ngam ГұiiЙ“al mum en."
  78,7,"Min mbaЙ—i pelle Й—e penЙ—e na haЙ—a leydi ndi dimmbaade."
  78,8,"Min tagi on onon yimЙ“e nooneeli: worЙ“e e rewЙ“e."
  78,9,"Min mbaЙ—i Й—oyngol mon taЖҙaade gah e golle ngam pooftaЙ—on."
  78,10,"Min mbaЙ—i jemma o ko cuuroowo on hono niЙ“e jemma mbo cuurdaton awraali mon."
  78,11,"Min mbaЙ—i Гұalawma o lefu faggitaade e yiilaade arsuka."
  78,12,"Min mahi dow mon kammuuli jeeЙ—iЙ—i cattuЙ—i mahnga ГұeeГұuЙ—i gollal."
  78,13,"Min mbaЙ—i naange nge lampu cattuЙ—a kuЙ“Й“am e njalbeendi."
  78,14,"Min tellini ummaade e duule potЙ—e toЙ“de ndiyam njuppajam sanne."
  78,15,"Ngam Min yaltina heen noone gabbe, e noone puЙ—i."
  78,16,"Min njaltina heen gese pilandirЙ—e leЙ“Й—Й— ngam naatandirde cate mum."
  78,17,"Pellet, Гұalawma ceerndugol hakkunde tagaaЙ—e laatiima ko ka dotta e waktu mbo luutndataako."
  78,18,"Г‘ande Malayka o wutti e allaadu he wuttannde Й—immere, ngaron-onon yimЙ“e- pelle pelle."
  78,19,"Kammu on uddite mbo wonta hono dame udditaaЙ—e."
  78,20,"Pelle Й—e mbaЙ—aa jahooje haa Й—e ngonti punndi nduuyndi, Й—e mba*i hono merere."
  78,21,"Pellet yiite jahannama nge wontii tommbii nge."
  78,22,"Nge wonanii bewЙ“e Й“e ruttorde kaЙ“e nduttato."
  78,23,"Й“e ГұiiЙ“a toon yontaaji Й—i ngalah happu."
  78,24,"Й“e meeЙ—atah toon henndu Й“uuЙ“ndu ustooru nguli Sa*iir, wonah ndiyam Й“uuЙ“Й—am kono dakmitire."
  78,25,"Й“e meeЙ—atah si wonah ndiyam ngulЙ—am jaw, e ЖҙiiЖҙiiri ciiwatoondi e yimЙ“e yiite."
  78,26,"Njobdi yaadundi e koЙ“e wonno ko e dow mum ummaade e keefeeru e majjere."
  78,27,"Pellet Й“e e aduna Й“e kulaano haasboore Alla ka laakira, sabu Й“e ngoonЙ—inaani ummital, siЙ“e ngoonЙ—inna ummital Й“e ngoonЙ—inatna Alla, Й“e golla ko moЖҙЖҙi."
  78,28,"Й“e penni aayeeje Amen tellinaaЙ—e e NelaaЙ—o Amen pennugol."
  78,29,"Kala huunde e golle mum en Min tonnggiЙ—e Min limi, tawa na winnda e Й—eri golle mum en."
  78,30,"MeeЙ—e -onon bewbe- Й—ee lepte duumiiЙ—e, Min Й“eydantah on si wonah lepte e dow lepte mon."
  78,31,"Pellet na woodani hulirЙ“e Alla siinude ko O yamiri e accude ko O haЙ—i, nokkere malal nde mbo Й“e ndaГұata faalee mum en ko Й—uum woni aljanna."
  78,32,"Gese e inabeeje."
  78,33,"E ЖҙoolnuЙ“e fotЙ“e duuЙ“i."
  78,34,"E kaas dolo keewЙ—o."
  78,35,"ЖҒe nanatah ka aljanna haala meere, wolla fenaande, Й“e penandirtah."
  78,36,"Й—um fof ko dokke Alla jonЙ—e."
  78,37,"jom kummuuli e leydi e ko woni hakkunde mum en, jurmotooЙ—o aduna e laakara, denndaangal ko woni e kammu e leydi ngalah hakke naamnaade Mbo si wonah O sakkitan Й“e Й—uum."
  78,38,"Г‘ande jibriil ummii tawa malayka en na waЙ—i saffeeli, Й“e haalatah e tefande hay gooto si wonah mbo jurmotooЙ—o sakkitani tefoore, o haala ko feewi, ko Й—uum woni konngol tawhiid."
  78,39,"Й—uum ko cifanaЙ—on woni Гұalngu mbo alah sikke gargol mammba, mbo faala daЙ—de e lepte Alla yo o nanngir laawol golle lobbe Й—e Alla welete faade heen."
  78,40,"Min njeertanii on-onon aade en- lepte Й“adiiЙ—e yande, Гұande aade ndaari ko gollunoo ko ka aduna, keefeero o wiya ngam wooЙ—eede iwde e lepte: haaniina mi wonta leydi hono no kulle Й—e nih, saanga nde Й—e mbiyate: ngontee leydi."
